Great quality & great classic ROCK !!

These guys don't have very many concerts left in them, so this one is definitely being added to the collection. 

Thanks for uploading it......will seed !!
Great resolution, bad encode. Video stutters throughout. It's noticeable whenever the camera pans. It's easy to see when the credits are rolling. I tried VLC and XBMC, it's the same.
@phase700b I guess it must be time for you to purchase a new PC Nothing wrong with this file dude

If someone is having problems viewing this file on a PC then your CPU is not capable of handling this file. Dont dump it, watch it with WD Media player or eventually when you get a new PC you will see that the fault lies there, not in this file.

Hey, great upload.
However, the video lags at several places.
Watch at 12:00 when Gibbons walks from the right to the left of the stage. Just passing the speaker sets, it looks like missing frames.

I've seen this using VLC at my PC and at my TV using the WDTV box.
